text: Rafael Peles (born 1936) is an Israeli former sports shooter. He competed in the 50 metre rifle, three positions and 50 metre rifle, prone events at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1936 births Category:Living people Category:Israeli male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Israel Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
